com.xing.api.data.profile

Class PhotoUrls

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xing.api.data.profile.PhotoUrls
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PhotoUrls
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Java representation of a user's picture/photo container. The XING API scales the user's profile picture in a different variety of sizes. This object allows the user to use any of the user's profile picture without scaling on the client side.
    See Also:
    User Profile Resource, Serialized Form
